{"tid":2515865,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：利君雅及刪片問題由聶德權及李百全負責 毋須徵他意見","createTime":"2021-05-04T09:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T09:48:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"541eec58e5b69799d90c0280edc38255998e3a27","tid":2515865,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"邱騰華稱利君雅不獲續約及港台刪影片均由部門處理<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華，回應港台助理節目主任利君雅不獲續約，以及港台刪除網上平台多條影片的問題時說，港台作為政府部門，在招聘人手方面，部門內應有規矩跟從，公務員事務局會提供意見，相信這方面最好交由部門處理。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華又說，港台如何處理以往拍攝的資料或節目，都是港台作為公營廣播機構及政府部門應自行執行的地方，毋須徵詢局方意見，相信港台會就這方面專業地按現時行之有效的方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有關與新加坡建立旅遊氣泡方面，邱騰華說會繼續留意雙方情況，如果疫情轉差會再磋商及審慎作決定，如穩定則會如期推行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589175-20210504.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589175-20210504.htm&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGno093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=b7e3dd5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589175-20210504.htm&h=fa27ad52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589175-20210504.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dae6383b140b7b41b64eca6e6da7cd8cccbb1ed8","tid":2515865,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"日治政府好野！"},{"pid":"5732bdd33d259e5170a08aa4cd8ffa289095c597","tid":2515865,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"共匪政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5c3a6444af9b4c49239aaa4c84461b737e8900","tid":2515865,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"Dklm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3d178c2da47e478a0902ed3144f3a00cbefedd","tid":2515865,"uid":15509